    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "On October 21, 1966, captioned individual telephonically",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "contacted the Bureau and spoke with SA [REDACTED] of the Crime",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "Research Section.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "11-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "He advised that he is a free-lance writer and is working",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "on a story for a TV production concerning unidentified flying objects.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "He stated that he has been in personal contact with a former Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "officer who uses the alias of [REDACTED] concerning unidentified flying",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "objects and that it is the TV producer's intention to use this individual",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "in the forthcoming TV show. He advised that [REDACTED] is not the individual's",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "true name and inquired as to whether the FBI could advise him of [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "real identity.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "[REDACTED] was advised that the FBI could not be of any",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "assistance to him and that all information in FBI files is confidential.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "He was also advised that the investigation of unidentified flying objects",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "is not, and never has been, a matter within the investigative jurisdiction",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "of the FBI.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "Bufiles contain no information which can be identified",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "with [REDACTED]",
